## Biography

Lionel Andres Messi is widely considered the greatest footballer of all time and one of the most transcendent athletes in any sport. Born in Rosario, Argentina, Messi moved to Barcelona at age 13 to treat a growth hormone deficiency that was threatening his football career. Barcelona paid for his medical treatment and gave him the platform to become the most complete player football has ever seen. Over 17 seasons at Barcelona, Messi won 10 La Liga titles, four UEFA Champions Leagues, seven Copa ...

