## Key Skills

- **Dribbling**: 100/100 - Possessed the ball like an extension of his body. Could change direction at full speed in ways that appeared to violate physics. The tightest dribbler in football history.
- **Vision & Playmaking**: 100/100 - Could see passes that other players couldn't imagine. Created goals for teammates at a rate that made him both the most goalscoring and most assisting player in Barcelona's history.
